#### <b>Heads up!</b> This unit starts with a pre-course survey. We appreciate your help in collecting crucial (and anonymous!) data about your students' beliefs and attitudes about computer science. The pre-course survey is about 30 questions long, so you may want to plan for it to be early homework or taken on an admin day before you being teaching. You can find more information about this pre-course survey in <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/csd1-2024/lessons/1" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lesson 1</a>.

